integratednbt:nbt_extractor.welcome.desc: This is a NBT Extractor. To start, place a variable of type NBT into the left slot.
integratednbt:nbt_extractor.loading.desc: Downloading content of this variable card...
integratednbt:nbt_extractor.error.eval: Failed to evaluate the provided variable.
integratednbt:nbt_extractor.error.type: Variable in the left slot must have type NBT.
integratednbt:nbt_extractor.error.unexpe: An unexpected error occurred. It is likely due to errors of either IntegratedDynamics or IntegratedNBT.
integratednbt:nbt_extractor.tooltip: §7Allows extraction of deeply nested values from a NBT typed variable.
integratednbt:nbt_extractor.tooltip.left: §8§o- Left click to extract this value
integratednbt:nbt_extractor.tooltip.sele: §aPath selected! Place a variable into the right slot to receive its value.
- In %s, output values are being created with a reference to the source NBT variable.
- In %s, the extraction process is encoded into an operator that accepts NBT and returns the extracted value.
- In %s, the value present is written to the output variable as a constant.
- In %s, the extraction process is encoded into a CyclopsCore NBT Path string.
Output Mode controls how the output value is being created.
If you don't understand this, stick with %s.
integratednbt:nbt_extractor.auto_refresh: §7Auto Refresh controls whether this NBT Extractor should automatically refresh the NBT tree when the source NBT variable is updated. You may freeze the current displaying NBT value by turning this option to §cOFF§7.
integratednbt:nbt_extractor_remote.bind_: Successfully bound remote to the NBT Extractor at (%s, %s, %s).
integratednbt:nbt_extractor_remote.need_: Please right click a NBT Extractor block to bind this remote first.
integratednbt:nbt_extractor_remote.requi: Previously bound NBT Extractor is not loaded on client-side. You need to be closer to the bound NBT Extractor. Chunk loading does NOT work.
Previously bound NBT Extractor is not loaded on the server.
Previously bound NBT Extractor is not in the same dimension.
integratednbt:nbt_extractor_remote.inval: Previously bound NBT Extractor no longer exists. Please right click another NBT Extractor block to bind again.
integratednbt:nbt_extractor_remote.toolt: §7Allows remote access of a NBT Extractor.
